==Upgrading== {{Upgrade dd-wrt}}
==Reverting== ===Reverting dd-wrt=== *[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?p=608849#608849 Source]
# Unplug ethernet & power cables # While holding down the reset button (bottom of router), plugin the power cable. Wait until the the power LED (blue) starts blinking. Let go of the reset button. Wait until the LED becomes steady. # Login to the router (192.168.1.1), go to Administration tab > Firmware upgrade, choose the "after Flashing, reset to" to Reset. # Choose original Firmware # Hit upgrade
Wait til it says Success and asks to login, leave login blank, password to "admin" (original Linksys default login).
